                    <span>This book will give you the perfect map for beginning your own seminar business whether you are experienced or not.  It also has so many references and tools that it will be the only book necessary regarding this  subject for you to have and keep.  Thank you Paul!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Wonderful way to learn more about how to get started!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
