                    <span>This book was really helpful to me. It contained information on everything from what to do with the initial idea of a seminar business, to how to write a great seminar brochure, to marketing techniques. Overall, I'd  HIGHLY recommend it to others interested in making money in the seminar  business. <p>Also, a good selling point is the listing of names, addresses,  and numbers for people in the business, contacts, good seminar locations,  etc. Very worthwhile investment!</span>
                  
              
